name: 2014 : : SATURDAY FEBRUARY 8TH : : 2014
description:
Join us for our first show of 2014!

DETAILS TO FOLLOW SHORTLY!

:: :: :: :: PLEASE NOTE :: :: :: ::

Tickets bought online will be AVAILABLE TO COLLECT ON THE CLUB DOOR ON THE NIGHT OF THE SHOW from 7pm.

Just take along a copy of your Paypal transaction receipt / a form of ID to collect your tickets.

Doors open at 8pm, Show starts at 9pm

:: :: :: :: :: :: :: :: :: :: :: :: :: :: ::

Standing tickets £12

Reserved Bench Seating £13.50 per ticket*

Reserved Table Seating £15 per ticket*

*Bench & Table seating is limited. It is now available on a first booked, first served basis. We try to seat large parties together - but due to the logistics of the venue - this may not always be possible. But we will try our best! Tables/benches may be shared with others. 
Seating is allocated - so if you are coming as a party - but have booked separately, we need to know this at the time of booking!

:: :: :: :: :: :: :: :: :: :: :: :: :: :: ::

Seating can ONLY be pre-booked here through The Wet Spot website.

Standing Tickets are available to buy in Leeds from The Wardrobe, Jumbo & Crash Records in the month leading up to the show, and on the door on the night

For more information please email thewetspotleeds@hotmail.co.uk

:: :: :: :: :: :: :: :: :: :: :: :: :: :: ::

All ticket sales are final. 
No returns, refunds or exchanges.
